videos.description: Jalen Smith makes a tough catch in traffic then dribbles around a defender to throw down the two-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Smith maneuvers in paint for Maryland slam) 2020/02/11

videos.headline: Smith maneuvers in paint for Maryland slam

videos.description: Anthony Cowan Jr. dishes to Darryl Morsell in the corner, who knocks down the 3-pointer to give Maryland a seven-point lead with just over a minute to play.
videos.headline: Morsell drains clutch 3 for Maryland

videos.description: Maryland's Anthony Cowan Jr. comes up with a steal on defense that leads to Aaron Wiggins' powerful two-handed flush on the fast break.
videos.headline: Wiggins throws down in transition
